CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 7, 1956, pg. 33, reads: "Cage Champs - The Cobras were winners of the fifth annual Junior Basketball Tournament held at Ammon Recreation Center. The defeated Arnold 56-47.  Front row, left to right, are Roger Thomas, Ralph Hughes and Eugene Harris.  Second row: Dan Brooks, Court Burrell and Tom Wallace. Rear: William Monroe, Coach Charles Betts and Embry Williams.  Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Cobras basketball team, front row from left: Roger Thomas, Ralph Hughes, Eugene Harris; second row: Dan Brooks, Court Burrell, Tom Wallace; rear: William Monroe, Coach Charles Betts, and Embry Williams, posed in gymnasium, another version
